+/**
+ *	ide_end_request		-	complete an IDE I/O
+ *	@drive: IDE device for the I/O
+ *	@uptodate: 
+ *	@nr_sectors: number of sectors completed
+ *
+ *	This is our end_request wrapper function. We complete the I/O
